{
  "stem": "19596.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 146.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was before, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I started to dig.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, make a hole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We dug a hole and there were four of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we dug hole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- and then I realized what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was digging my own grave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was so drunk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said he wanted to shoot us in the grave and said, a German bullet is too good for you [INAUDIBLE] Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he put it back and walked away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A German bullet is not-- is too good for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The four of us stood there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- and the infamous one I met was a fellow called Pohl, P-O-H-L.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was in charge, second to Hitler, administration and economics of the SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He ran the Politische Abteilung in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was often there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was tried in the Nuremberg trial and he was hung.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he came to the SS laundry and I delivered-- I delivered to his house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I was sorting-- sorting from people who were gassed-- I was sorting their belongings, their clothes and their things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were disinfecting it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Zyklon B was thrown in-- and the same gas they killed the-- killed the people with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after about 15, 20 minutes, they put the fans on and we were going in with gas masks to remove the clothes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The clothes were sorted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, blouse by blouse and suit by suit and this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were sent to Germany, to the Winterhilfe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what the Winterhilfe is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To help poor people in Germany or bombed-out people with clothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There also-- also in about I think it was also '43.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was before the laundry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
